    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1899-01-21T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1899-01-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="190"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d190">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hart</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-01-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 21, 1899</hi> (January 23,
                        1899)</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Referring to the Panama claim, have accepted offer to pay $30,000 in three equal
                    installments, February 10, April 10, and June 10, in drafts at sixty days. Best
                    that could be done in desperate financial situation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hart.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
